00:48:32,210 --> 00:48:33,344
[MC] Wasn't she great?

777
00:48:33,378 --> 00:48:34,712
Chelsea, let's give
it up for Chelsea.

778
00:48:34,745 --> 00:48:36,314
Great girl, nice act.

779
00:48:36,347 --> 00:48:40,018
And now, next, he's your
favorite ventriloquist,

780
00:48:40,051 --> 00:48:41,286
Mr. John Peasy.

781
00:48:43,854 --> 00:48:46,357
Hey, folks, my name is John
Peasy, this is my friend Smokey.

782
00:48:46,391 --> 00:48:48,593
Holy shit, they're all white!

783
00:48:48,626 --> 00:48:50,361
Okay, we have a great
crowd of people here.

784
00:48:50,395 --> 00:48:52,197
Yeah, they look good, this
look good, I like it, like it.

785
00:48:52,230 --> 00:48:53,131
Yeah, we got a good crowd.

786
00:48:53,164 --> 00:48:54,232
I'm the only black guy here.

